commit.message:
Merge Allow any characters after expected MM header

This merge allows any characters (esp. `\r`) after the expected matrix market header. Additionally, if the regex search failed, the description line is also printed.

Related PR: https://github.com/ginkgo-project/ginkgo/pull/1557

Merge improved templated matrix constructors and `create` functions

This replaces `EnableCreateMethod` by explicit (documented) `create` functions and
removes templated `array` constructors by explicit parameters, with a deprecated
`initializer_list` overload for interface-stability.

Related PR: https://github.com/ginkgo-project/ginkgo/pull/1433
